schools.name: Robert E. Lee Junior High School

data.description: Nestled in the sought-after Forsythe neighborhood, this 4 bed 2.5 bath home is tucked away in a quiet cul-de-sac situated on half acre! Step into the formal living and dining area to be met with stunning hardwood floors. The spacious family room with a fireplace invites for cozy gatherings, and the kitchen boasts an island bar. The large fenced-in backyard offers plenty of space for gardening. Turn this open patio and enclosed porch into the haven for relaxation! Create lasting memories in your own slice of paradise!
